        "Given the  nonzero steady states have not been calculated explicitly, we proceed using graphical analysis of stability. In @fig-sprucebudworm-rhsfg  (b) we plot the right-hand side of @eq-budwormnondim against $n$ and examine the cases of large, small and intermediate $r$ for a given value of $q$. \n",
